when the love is gone is a 2013 filipino romantic drama film directed by andoy ranay , starring cristine reyes , gabby concepcion , alice dixson , andi eigenmann , and jake cuenca .   the film is distributed by viva films with co-production of multivision pictures and was released november 27 , 2013 nationwide as part of viva films ' 32nd anniversary .   the movie is a remake of the 1983 blockbuster movie nagalit ang buwan sa haba ng gabi by danny zialcita which stars laurice guillen , gloria diaz , dindo fernando , janice de belen , and eddie garcia .